{"tid":1909000,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(必撐)難得有一套又黃又好睇既港劇-二月廿九","createTime":"2020-03-03T16:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T14:45:41.000Z","uid":262593,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"063b6c3c02f2e4b3bdc03e36890f5dc2c9c54db9","tid":1909000,"uid":262593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"(非行動POST)<br />\n演員黃到發金- 徐天佑、劉俊謙、岑珈其<br />\n依家肯發聲既藝人已經賣少見少 一發聲就等於無得上大陸發展 所以香港人一定要撐<br />\n<br />\n我一開電視睇到已經覺得驚為天人,第一次睇到畫面咁靚既港劇,基本上已經係電影既級數。<br />\n加上演員由上一套&lt;教束&gt;已經好鍾意,今次基本上原班人馬 但完全另外一個感覺! <br />\n<br />\n游大東【鴻鵠志－影視筆記】:2020年第一套極期待港劇，終於出現！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yautaitung/videos/505391096828738/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyautaitung%2Fvideos%2F505391096828738%2F&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=22b68aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yautaitung/videos/505391096828738/</a><br />\n鹿米館:終於有套識打燈港劇《二月廿九》<br />\n<a href=\"http://lunkayun.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flunkayun.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fblog-post.html%3Fm%3D1&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=1b07881f\" target=\"_blank\">http://lunkayun.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwS8St2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwS8St2.png&h=2967d4b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puzfxt2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpuzfxt2.png&h=9cb2f64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRy0JAJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRy0JAJ.jpg&h=21d25c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持 壯大黃色影視圈!"},{"pid":"0ba6ae275d910c6d21de3e182783dc5f6d7525a9","tid":1909000,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:05:07.000Z","msg